news related:
We are considering making something to assist people in regards to reading the news. Often, news is sporadic and unrelated, and multiple sources have different biases, and as such they are causing people to become polarized because they read very different news stories. Our project is going to attempt to address this by creating a reccomended readings (similar to book sites such as goodreads or reccomendations for shows) based on news articles people have read. This way, they can focus on one topic and become more well learned. For example, if someone is reading something on the current news in Iran it will reccomend older articles that give background context such as the lead up to the conflict, why there is friction between the countries, and other articles showing different stuff left out of the article. 


